  "title": "EDA Specialist",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a IC Design startup that design chips for optical technology to improve speed, reliability, and energy use in modern systems is seeking for IT Engineer (EDA Tools)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>EDA Specialist</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking a skilled and proactive <strong>EDA Specialist </strong>to maintain and enhance the mission-critical IT environment that supports our chip design (R&amp;D) teams. You will be responsible for the entire EDA tool ecosystem, ensuring high availability, security, and performance to enable our engineers to design world-class products.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>install, update, and fix the engineering design software (EDA tools) and their licenses.</li>\n  <li>Watch over our computer servers and fix any problems quickly.</li>\n  <li>Create automated systems to make the engineers' work easier and faster.</li>\n  <li>Write scripts and help with tasks on our Linux systems.</li>\n  <li>Work directly with our design teams to solve their IT issues and find solutions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure our systems are secure and follow company rules.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's degree and 5 years' experience directly related to the duties specified above in an IT environment.</li>\n  <li>Good Communicator, strong analytical and problem solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Working knowledge of Unix/Linux environment. Familiar with <strong>SGE/LSF job</strong> scheduler.</li>\n  <li>Working knowledge of<strong> EDA license management.</strong></li>\n  <li>Working knowledge of <strong>EDA software administration and installation.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of version control software, such as Git/Gerrit/Jenkins/ClearCase.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants, kindly send in a copy of your updated resume in WORD document to <strong>venus@searchstaffing.com.sg</strong>stating your current and expected remuneration together with notice period required to current employer.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 12C6254 | EA Personnel Registration No: R1879665</p>",
